{% comment %}
  TASK: 10 — Badge % OFF: ((compare_at - price) * 100) / compare_at | round; só se compare_at > price > 0 e available.
  Texto via `products.product.percent_off`. Na PDP o bloco de preço é re-renderizado no servidor ao mudar variante (product-info.js).
  Parâmetros: compare_at_price, price, available (boolean)
{% endcomment %}
{% liquid
  assign pct = 0
  if available and compare_at_price > price and compare_at_price > 0
    assign pct = compare_at_price | minus: price | times: 100 | divided_by: compare_at_price | round
  endif
%}
{% if pct > 0 %}
  {{- 'products.product.percent_off' | t: percent: pct -}}
{% endif %}
